==========================================================================================================

Booleans and Boolean objects cannot be safely compared.



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<p id="demo"></p>
<script>
const x = new Boolean(false);
const y = new Boolean(false);
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = (x==y);
</script>    
</body>    
</html>


